---
title: Sweet Potato and Courgette Salad with crunchy croutons and crumbled Greek style cheese
description: This warm veg salad is adorned with all sorts of wonderful things. Crispy croutons, softened onion and salty Greek style cheese are just a few factors in this delicious and healthy dish.
